plugins.rule_description.rule_page.5.lor:

Unsolicited attacking or killing of players (outside PVP zones); harassment like trapping players or blocking their Nether Portals.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.6: Respect, be friendly, be inclusive, keep the community clean.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.6.lor:
Examples:
Spamming, arguing, or using offensive language in public chat.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.7: If you love to complain about this environment, then leave.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.7.lor: We welcome all positive members to the community and hope to maintain an enjoyable environment together.
